    "Name": "Vandal",
    "Details": "The Vandal LI-OT configuration is focused on command and support roles. Armed with a Snub-nose PPC and a Large X-Pulse Laser, the 'Mech can still do decent damage. Two Laser AMS provides self-defense, while a C3 Master helps tying the lance's C3 network together. The Angel ECM of the primary configuration was kept, and a Bloodhound Active Probe added.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Variable Range Targeting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>\n\n",
